assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"Apple/Google ecosystem<br />\n<a href=\"https://char.gd/blog/2018/google-is-eating-apples-ecosystem-for-lunch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchar.gd%2Fblog%2F2018%2Fgoogle-is-eating-apples-ecosystem-for-lunch&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=a122ebf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://char.gd/blog/2018/google-is-eating-apples-ecosystem-for-lunch</a><br />\n<br />\n2FA for Apple ID<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204915#howitworks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT204915%23howitworks&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=30ecd625\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204915#howitworks</a><br />\n<br />\n一般用戶能掌握2FA固然最理想<br />\n如果IT狗容易support一般用戶也不錯<br />\n<br />\n但Google&rsquo;s ecosystem的痛處<br />\n是缺乏自家硬體/endpoints<br />\n每每寄人籬下（靠裝agent/app）"}]}